renderpass.code:
#define mainImage(O,U)  \
	vec3 p, R =iResolution, d = normalize( vec3(U - R.xy/2., R) );  \
    float i=0., m;  \
	while(i++ < 90.){  \
        m = 1. - length(p.xy) + texture(iChannel0, vec2(p.z + iTime, atan(d.x, d.y)) / 6.28).r;  \
        p += d * m/3.;  \
		if(m < .01)break;}  \
	O += 1.-  i / 90.
renderpass.name: Image
